{"tid":729630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"所有野都係假...","createTime":"2018-07-04T17:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T17:32:39.000Z","uid":187197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b649e436c7213e1737ef689338ce391b16e254e4","tid":729630,"uid":187197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"一齊咗差唔多一年<br />\n原來同我一齊只係因為可以洗我啲錢<br />\n我唔係有錢人<br />\n一個月得萬幾蚊又要比屋企仲要養埋佢<br />\n我個個月尾都窮到要朋友請食飯<br />\n一路以黎我以為佢對我係真<br />\n又話結婚又見咗家長<br />\n到今日...先有個common fd話其實佢識我男朋友之前兩個ex<br />\n之前兩個ex都覺得呢個人好奇怪，成日問佢地借錢所以飛咗佢<br />\n我同佢已經個幾兩個月冇見<br />\n我仲一路呃自己其實佢好忙所以見唔到<br />\n今日先清楚明白原來所有野都係假<br />\n我係on9，比佢呃咗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢已經喺我世界消失...可能係因為佢已經揾到第二條水魚..."},{"pid":"630b9d952e99dbcd9ebd6f0f84dbfacf5211beb6","tid":729630,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪on9，有幾忙可以兩個月唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3833d1d9d6f5b9f050bc3dad3ef7cb1dee34e70e","tid":729630,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"你是一個西洞"},{"pid":"564e4d05bbfdebdb65c6992c2e79f8a885b1dc8f","tid":729630,"uid":144325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:29:33.000Z","msg":"風花月似戲一場"},{"pid":"8151113589c132793255f1930cb73867cc3014d8","tid":729630,"uid":187197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"630b9d952e99dbcd9ebd6f0f84dbfacf5211beb6","tid":729630,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪on9，有幾忙可以兩個月唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:32:39.000Z","msg":"我信佢<br />\n所以我on9"}]}